text: The code above is a simple web application that allows users to upload files to the server. The code above is vulnerable to a directory traversal attack. The code above is vulnerable to a directory traversal attack because the code does not check the file name of the file that is being uploaded. This means that an attacker can upload a file with a name like ../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../
